Package: nat.hdf5
Type: Package
Title: Read Neuron Data from HDF5 files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(
    person("Philipp", "Schlegel", email = "uni.matrix742@gmail.com", 
      role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5633-1314"))
    )
Maintainer: Philipp Schlegel <pms70@cam.ac.uk>
URL: https://github.com/schlegelp/nat.hdf5
Description: This package lets you read and write neurons from/to HDF5 files. 
    It's capable of working with multiple different representations (skeletons,
    dotprops, meshes) and generic annotations (e.g. synapses) of the same 
    neuron. A description of the schema can be found here:
    https://github.com/schlegelp/navis/blob/master/docs/source/hdf5_format.md
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1),
Imports:
    nat (>= 1.10.0),  
    hdf5r (>= 1.3.3),
    rgl,
    progress
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr    
